OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775289888
OL,3,CPM calls for 'community over division'
OL,4,Cin Easter message of 'renewal'
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has said Britain is
OL,7,Fbest when it chooses "community over
OL,8,Fdivision" in an Easter message
OL,9,Facknowledging a moment of "real
OL,10,Fanxiety" as the Iran war hits the UK
OL,11,Feconomy and pushes up costs.
OL,13,FThe prime minister said faith could
OL,14,Foffer "reassurance and grounding" at a
OL,15,Ftime of uncertainty and paid tribute
OL,16,Fto churches across the country for
OL,17,Fsupporting families and bringing
OL,18,Fpeople together.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775289888
OL,3,CPM calls for 'community over division'
OL,4,Cin Easter message of 'renewal'
OL,6,FHe added: "In times when some seek to
OL,7,Fdivide, the Government is committed to
OL,8,Fworking across faiths and differences
OL,9,Fto build a country that is more
OL,10,Fresilient, inclusive and connected."
OL,12,FBritons are braced for a cost-of-
OL,13,Fliving squeeze as conflict in the
OL,14,FMiddle East and a blockade on the
OL,15,FStrait of Hormuz, through which around
OL,16,Fa fifth of the world's oil and gas is
OL,17,Fshipped, sends global oil prices
OL,18,Fskyrocketing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775289888
OL,3,CPM calls for 'community over division'
OL,4,Cin Easter message of 'renewal'
OL,6,FFuel duty is frozen until September,
OL,7,Fwith the increase scheduled for then
OL,8,Funder review as a result of the high
OL,9,Fprices, and average household energy
OL,10,Fbills are predicted to rise when
OL,11,FOfgem's current price cap expires at
OL,12,Fthe end of June.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,19,FIn his Easter message, Sir Keir said:
OL,20,F"Easter is a celebration of hope, new
OL,21,Flife and renewal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775289888
OL,3,CPM calls for 'community over division'
OL,4,Cin Easter message of 'renewal'
OL,6,F"Across the country, churches and
OL,7,FChristian communities quietly and
OL,8,Ftirelessly support families, children
OL,9,Fand neighbours ` offering comfort,
OL,10,Fbringing people together, and standing
OL,11,Falongside those who need it most.
OL,13,F"It is precisely that spirit of
OL,14,Fservice which exemplifies national
OL,15,Frenewal, and reflects the very heart
OL,16,Fof Christ's example.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775289888
OL,3,CPM calls for 'community over division'
OL,4,Cin Easter message of 'renewal'
OL,6,F"This Easter comes at a time of real
OL,7,Fanxiety for many people. Conflicts
OL,8,Fabroad, pressures at home, and
OL,9,Funcertainty about the future weigh
OL,10,Fheavily on families and households.
OL,12,F"In moments like these, faith offers
OL,13,Freassurance and grounding ` a reminder
OL,14,Fthat we are not alone, and that hope
OL,15,Fcan still take root even in difficult
OL,16,Fsoil."
OL,26,@xD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775289888
OL,3,CPM calls for 'community over division'
OL,4,Cin Easter message of 'renewal'
OL,6,FThe prime minister added: "Our country
OL,7,Fis at its best when we choose
OL,8,Fcommunity over division, kindness over
OL,9,Findifference, and service over
OL,10,Fselfinterest.
OL,12,F"I thank everyone who gives their time
OL,13,Fthrough churches and Christian
OL,14,Fcharities, and wish Christians across
OL,15,Fthe UK and around the world a very
OL,16,Fhappy Easter filled with peace, hope
OL,17,Fand the promise of new life."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775289888
OL,3,CPM calls for 'community over division'
OL,4,Cin Easter message of 'renewal'
OL,6,FTory Opposition leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,7,Falso offered a hopeful message,
OL,8,Fdescribing Easter as "a reminder that
OL,9,Feven in the darkest times, renewal is
OL,10,Fpossible and that light can overcome
OL,11,Fdarkness".
OL,13,F"At the heart of the Christian faith
OL,14,Fis a story of redemption, of second
OL,15,Fchances, of perseverance and of the
OL,16,Fbelief that better days lie ahead,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1775289888
OL,3,CPM calls for 'community over division'
OL,4,Cin Easter message of 'renewal'
OL,6,F"In a world that can often feel
OL,7,Funcertain, perhaps even bleak, with
OL,8,Fconflicts in the Middle East and
OL,9,FUkraine, and challenges at home, that
OL,10,Fmessage matters more than ever.
OL,12,F"Across the country, we also see the
OL,13,Fcultural value of Christianity in the
OL,14,Fquiet, everyday impact of that faith
OL,15,Fin acts of kindness, service and
OL,16,Fsacrifice in our communities. I wish
OL,17,FChristians and all people across the
OL,18,FUnited Kingdom a very happy Easter."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
